title: Carb Smart Double Chicken Bulgur Bowls with DIY Jalapeño Ranch Dressing
description: Jalapeño ranch dressing steals the show in this quick and well-balanced bowl. Smoky baked chicken pairs perfectly with the creamy ranch, while lemony bulgur brings pops of brightness to every bite!

